data.name: ShortcutToggle_Description
data.value: Key to Press to toggle the characters menu.

data.name: ModuleDescription
data.value: A tool to easily switch characters even with a lot of them! This will require an API-Key with permissions at least for the 'characters' endpoint!

data.name: LoginAfterSelect
data.value: Enter the game automatically after selecting the character in the character selection

data.name: UISizeDisclaimer
data.value: You will have to set the games Interface Size to 'Larger' to get the correct cut outs!

data.name: FocusFilter_Description
data.value: When toggling the main menu to show, automatically focus the search field

data.name: SearchGuide
data.value: -c Crafting Profession -p Profession/Specialization -r Race -b Birthday -m MapName -t CustomTag -c Chef; -p Warrior will show all warriors and all chefs

data.name: SwapModifier_Description
data.value: Only if the Modifier is pressed trigger character swapping. This will prevent accidientally swapping!

data.name: EnterToLogin_Description
data.value: If the searchbox is focused pressing 'RETURN' will log to the first character in the list.

data.name: EnterOnSwap_Description
data.value: Enter the game automatically after selecting the character in the character selection

data.name: Error_InvalidPermissions
data.value: This API key does not have the required permissions.

data.name: FilterDelay_Description
data.value: Average time in milliseconds waited between filtering your characters' panel. To get the current value you will have to swap module tabs once to update the settings page!

data.name: OnlyMaxCrafting_Description
data.value: Show only crafts that are at a 500 rank (Jeweler & Scribe at 400).

data.name: OnlyMaxCrafting_DisplayName
data.value: Show only maxed out crafting Professions

data.name: SwapDelay_Description
data.value: Avg. loading time from ingame to character selection. To get the current value you will have to swap module tabs once to update the settings page!

data.name: FadeOut_Description
data.value: Fade the filter and character window automatically after 2500 ms

data.name: Error_Competivive
data.value: Character swapping is disabled in competition mode!

data.name: LogoutDescription
data.value: Key to Press to open the logout menu. Must be the same as the game keybind for 'Logout'!

data.name: AutoLogin_Description
data.value: If enabled on the first load of Blish and beeing in character selection the module enters the game. After entering the game it will wait until the MumbleLink and API Token is fully loaded. Once fully loaded it will switch to the character which is set to be the "Login Character".

data.name: DoubleClickToEnter_Description
data.value: Enables double clicking the character in the character list to login to that character.
